            <title><![CDATA[【注意！#高温天猛吃冷饮易诱发脑卒中#[吃惊]】多地气温超40℃。高温天人的情绪波动较大，或致血压异常波动，还有猛吃冷饮、喝冰水等，都可能诱发脑卒中，俗称“...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【注意！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%A9%E5%A4%A9%E7%8C%9B%E5%90%83%E5%86%B7%E9%A5%AE%E6%98%93%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E8%84%91%E5%8D%92%E4%B8%AD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%A9%E5%A4%A9%E7%8C%9B%E5%90%83%E5%86%B7%E9%A5%AE%E6%98%93%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E8%84%91%E5%8D%92%E4%B8%AD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#高温天猛吃冷饮易诱发脑卒中#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】多地气温超40℃。高温天人的情绪波动较大，或致血压异常波动，还有猛吃冷饮、喝冰水等，都可能诱发脑卒中，俗称“脑梗死”。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23120%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E6%B3%95%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E8%84%91%E5%8D%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AD%E6%9A%91%23&amp;extparam=%23120%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E6%B3%95%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E8%84%91%E5%8D%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AD%E6%9A%91%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#120识别法快速分辨脑卒中和中暑#</span></a>：1看，一张脸不对称，口角歪；2查，两只手臂单侧无力，不能抬；0（聆）听，说话口齿不清，不明白。若以上症状突然发生，应立即送医！👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4915869084745765" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hf8cvslb1cj61in0uq1k302.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/6MCPl4Vglx086sTdw88U01041200sgYh0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1687741310&amp;ssig=uNsRkMqo3e&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/iSJZCYEXlx086sTddAtO01041200eS6v0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1687741310&amp;ssig=rtDkiD2%2Fno&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/yFUeLQlMlx086sTcyR32010412009y1G0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1687741310&amp;ssig=4ihD7V1Jiv&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4915869084745765&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
